claim.claim-text:
An information processing device (10) characterized by comprising:
a processor (111);
a volatile memory (113); and
a ROM (116) storing firmware including a basic input output system (BIOS),
wherein the processor (111) is configured to execute firmware instructions of:
connecting the information processing device (10) to a first server (20) through a network;
downloading a client program from the first server (20) into the volatile memory (113), the client program configured to communicate with a second server (30) which provides a virtual desktop environment, and to receive a virtual desktop image from the second server (30);
launching the client program in order to connect the information processing device (10) to the second server (30) through the network; and
turning off the power of the information processing device (10) to erase content in the volatile memory (113), when the information processing device (10) is disconnected from the network after the connection between the information processing device (10) and the second server (30) is established.

An operation control method of controlling an operation of an information processing device (10) executed by firmware stored in a ROM (116) in the information processing device (10), the operation control method characterized by comprising:
connecting the information processing device (10) to a first server (20) through a network;
downloading a client program from the first server (20) into a volatile memory (113) in the information processing device (10), the client program configured to communicate with a second server (30) which provides a virtual desktop environment, and receive a virtual desktop image from the second server (30);
launching the client program in order to connect the information processing device (10) to the second server (30) through the network; and
turning off the power of the information processing device (10) to erase content in the volatile memory (113), when the information processing device (10) is disconnected from the network after the connection between the information processing device (10) and the second server (30) is established.
